Classes in rs.ac.ns.ftn.tmd.fuzzy.membershipFunction that implement LRMembershipFunction
 class LRMembershipFunctionExponential
          Exponential membership function

In fact, this is quasi-exponential function, with cut-off point at 4.5 * variance

m_f (X) = exp ( -X / variance ); if 0 < x <= 4.5*variance
m_f (X) = 0 ; if x> 4.5*variance
 class LRMembershipFunctionGaussian
          Gaussian membership function

in fact, this is quasi-Gaussian function with cut-off at 3*variance
m_f (X) = exp ( -X^2 / (2* variance^2 ); if 0 < x <= 3*variance
m_f (X) = 0 ; if x> 3*variance

 class LRMembershipFunctionQuadratic
          Quadratic membership function
m_f (X) = 1 - X^2 / spread^2
